# Start from latest `main`

Before making or committing changes in this repo:

1. Run **`git fetch origin`** and ensure your branch is aligned with **`origin/main`** (e.g. `git status` should not show your tracking branch as **behind** `origin/main`).
2. If you are behind: **`git pull --rebase origin main`** while on `main`, or **rebase/merge `origin/main` into your feature branch** before piling on new commits.
3. Avoid long-lived drift from **`adampadobe/AEP-Orchestration-Lab`** **`main`** without coordinating with your teammate.

Upstream is **`origin`** → `https://github.com/adampadobe/AEP-Orchestration-Lab.git`.
